{"tid":1319291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實覺得白色嗰班先最癲，藍色都算做緊磨心","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:29:36.000Z","uid":185710,"like":129,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf5fc9f230d500483d812bc72496be0ce1e259f","tid":1319291,"uid":185710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，聯想起以前有藍色差佬同我講白色嗰班好L多PK，而我是認同的。其實我覺得大家應該目標明確對準白色，拉攏藍色嗰班。真心講繼續而家呢個情況，肯定會無限loop。<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家有無發現好似大部分情況下，白色都癲過藍色。如果大家望返會發覺白色發癲比例好鬼高。之前發癲嗰班都大部分都大sir黎<br />\n<br />\n純想大家暫時冷靜一下。不分割。"},{"pid":"84f0fc54e48be3c81e503c9014e7e4499447aadc","tid":1319291,"uid":28227,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"無分別，一樣癲"},{"pid":"0c2d60bb359c209d204b2d7e53b6689f8a24edb1","tid":1319291,"uid":185710,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"84f0fc54e48be3c81e503c9014e7e4499447aadc","tid":1319291,"uid":28227,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"無分別，一樣癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"拿 我認同藍色都暴力啊不過想大家正視白色先重點黎 白色PK程度肯肯定定藍色十幾倍以上"},{"pid":"2014c40e74b9a97e602e842f46d3108c36ead6f3","tid":1319291,"uid":255690,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0c2d60bb359c209d204b2d7e53b6689f8a24edb1","tid":1319291,"uid":185710,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"84f0fc54e48be3c81e503c9014e7e4499447aadc","tid":1319291,"uid":28227,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"無分別，一樣癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"拿 我認同藍色都暴力啊不過想大家正視白色先重點黎 白色PK程度肯肯定定藍色十幾倍以上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"上又唔洗佢地上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c946ac64e6308352ef7f2fd68eda8a759cd44f","tid":1319291,"uid":195714,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KG0EngG.gif